message: Hi Bob, I'm selling a product that I think you'll find very valuable. I'm offering it to you for $95.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am only able to pay up to $85 for it.
I understand you're looking for a good deal, Bob. How about we meet in the middle at $90?
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. However, I am still unable to go above $85 for this product.
